{"tid":1192204,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"習主席差少少仆親!!!","createTime":"2019-06-08T10:02:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T17:30:23.000Z","uid":66271,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"74f6115211be973add524f38d9aa70241312f6d9","tid":1192204,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T10:02:30.000Z","msg":"中國國家主席習近平近日訪問俄羅斯，與「知心好友」俄羅斯總統普丁會晤，周五（7日）共同出席聖彼得堡國際經濟論壇。原本一切進展順利，沒想到會議中卻發生了一段小插曲，習近平與台下參與者親切握手時，一個不小心竟然失去平衡，差點摔倒。<br />\n<br />\n聖彼得堡國際經濟論壇討論完最後一道問題後，參與者自在地在會場中交談，台上的領袖及嘉賓們也相互握手致意，習近平滿臉笑容地與在場人士親切互動，並轉身到台邊向台下來賓問好，有人開心上前與他握手，也有人拿出手機想與習近平自拍。<br />\n沒想到不知是參加者握得太用力了，還是習近平沒站好，只見習近平突然一個重心不穩往前傾倒，所幸旁邊的聯邦警衛局（Federal Guard Service）保鑣立刻扶住他，才沒有讓習近平當場跌倒。他之後在台上繼續向大家揮手致意。<br />\n<br />\n片 ：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/dimsmirnov175/status/1137015918440132610?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdimsmirnov175%2Fstatus%2F1137015918440132610%3Fs%3D20&d=Wvd4d0Ghp%2Fc8oQdY%2BKiOSXKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=c5236922\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdimsmirnov175%2Fstatus%2F1137015918440132610%3Fs%3D20&h=04678dee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/dimsmirnov175/status/1137015918440132610?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"a6a80d5cb32af307754e6a19890c568263f44ebc","tid":1192204,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T10:02:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f479e970cfc988d2bd3e84b7e9c0fa0641617f","tid":1192204,"uid":66271,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"a6a80d5cb32af307754e6a19890c568263f44ebc","tid":1192204,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T10:02:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T10:04:00.000